    "field_attribution_instructions": [
        {
            "format": "basic_html",
            "processed": "<h3>How do I cite SNT?</h3>  <p><strong>Note that neither the main <a href=\"/software/fiji#publication\">Fiji article</a>, nor the first <a href=\"#what-is-the-difference-between-snt-and-simple-neurite-tracer\">Simple Neurite Tracer</a> publication are appropriate citations for SNT. The proper citation for SNT is</strong>:</p>  <ul>   <li><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1038/s41592-021-01105-7\">doi:10.1038/s41592-021-01105-7</a></li> </ul>  <p>In addition, you should also cite any additional modules that you may use:</p>  <ul>   <li><strong><a href=\"/plugins/snt/sholl\">Sholl Analysis</a></strong> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1038/nmeth.3125\">doi:10.1038/nmeth.3125</a></li>   <li><strong><a href=\"/plugins/snt/modeling\">Cx3D</a></strong> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3389/neuro.10.025.2009\">doi:10.3389/neuro.10.025.2009</a></li>   <li><strong><a href=\"/plugins/snt/extending#tubular-geodesics\">Tubular Geodesics</a></strong> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/cvpr.2012.6247722\">doi:10.1109/cvpr.2012.6</a></li></ul>",
            "value": "<h3>How do I cite SNT?</h3>  <p><strong>Note that neither the main <a href=\"/software/fiji#publication\">Fiji article</a>, nor the first <a href=\"#what-is-the-difference-between-snt-and-simple-neurite-tracer\">Simple Neurite Tracer</a> publication are appropriate citations for SNT. The proper citation for SNT is</strong>:</p>  <ul>   <li><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1038/s41592-021-01105-7\">doi:10.1038/s41592-021-01105-7</a></li> </ul>  <p>In addition, you should also cite any additional modules that you may use:</p>  <ul>   <li><strong><a href=\"/plugins/snt/sholl\">Sholl Analysis</a></strong> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1038/nmeth.3125\">doi:10.1038/nmeth.3125</a></li>   <li><strong><a href=\"/plugins/snt/modeling\">Cx3D</a></strong> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3389/neuro.10.025.2009\">doi:10.3389/neuro.10.025.2009</a></li>   <li><strong><a href=\"/plugins/snt/extending#tubular-geodesics\">Tubular Geodesics</a></strong> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/cvpr.2012.6247722\">doi:10.1109/cvpr.2012.6"
